when I saw this happening:

00:02:46.852 --> 00:02:51.121
the biggest surge in nationalist votes
in Western democracies

00:02:51.145 --> 00:02:52.643
since World War II.

00:02:53.413 --> 00:02:56.388
All of a sudden,
this isn't theory anymore.

